I just celebrated my 37th year of #sobriety and thought I should pass along a positive message to anyone out there who might be struggling with that issue.  I don’t miss drinking and all the hazy and unhealthy episodes that go along with it. I feel fortunate to practice #soberliving. I don’t judge people who enjoy alcohol but I will say quitting alcohol changed my life for the better.  While I don’t go to meetings any more as part of my sobriety if you are struggling 90 meetings in 90 days is a great way to start the journey 💕 #aa #billw #addiction #alcoholrecovery #12steps #recovery #recoveryispossible
